,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3570976,"name":"Jeffrey Davis","username":"Practicality","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/practicality/{size}/208492_2.png","created_at":"2025-03-28T04:52:10.575Z","cooked":"<p>Put this code in the periodic of the elevator subsystem instead of in a while loop. It will do exactly the same logic 50 times a second. If you’re using time-based and/or don’t have subsystems, do it in teleop periodic whenever a go-to position state is active.</p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":5,"updated_at":"2025-03-28T04:52:10.575Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":45,"readers_count":44,"score":9.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":497195,"topic_slug":"presets","display_username":"Jeffrey Davis","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":62548,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/presets/497195/4","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3570979,"name":"Jeffrey Davis","username":"Practicality","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/practicality/{size}/208492_2.png","created_at":"2025-03-28T04:55:36.921Z","cooked":"<p>Check out our Elevator code for doing this. It has both updates 1 and 2 that <a class="mention" href="/u/archduketim">@ArchdukeTim</a> describes: <a href="https://github.com/jeffreyddavis/frc2025/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Elevator.java" class="inline-onebox">frc2025/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Elevator.java at master · jeffreyddavis/frc2025 · GitHub</a></p>
<p>Near the bottom is the calculateOutput and the periodic. That should be all you need</p>
<p>For the basic set up you could forego the <span class="abbreviation">PID<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Proportional Integral Derivative"></template></span> controller and just do your -.1 and +.1 logic to see how it works. You could then add <span class="abbreviation">PID<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Proportional Integral Derivative"></template></span> back in to get something smoother.</p>
<p>So in my code for calculateOutput you would just put your logic that returns either a .1 a 0 or a -.1</p>
<p>Edit: I realize that you’re doing more of an arm/wrist. This code might be closer to what you’re doing. Same ideas though: <a href="https://github.com/jeffreyddavis/frc2025/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Arm.java" class="inline-onebox">frc2025/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Arm.java at master · jeffreyddavis/frc2025 · GitHub</a></p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":5,"updated_at":"2025-03-28T05:07:39.925Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":3,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":44,"readers_count":43,"score":8.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":497195,"topic_slug":"presets","display_username":"Jeffrey Davis","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":2,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"https://github.com/jeffreyddavis/frc2025/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Elevator.java","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"frc2025/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Elevator.java at master · jeffreyddavis/frc2025 · GitHub","clicks":4},{"url":"https://github.com/jeffreyddavis/frc2025/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Arm.java","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"frc2025/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/Arm.java at master · jeffreyddavis/frc2025 · GitHub","clicks":1}],"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":74572,"username":"Myles","name":"","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/779978/{size}.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":62548,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/presets/497195/5","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"curren